    • Method Detail

      • selftest

        List<Selftest.SelftestResult> selftest(String module)
        Executes the selftests for the given module. WebDriver generally has a blocking API so this method will return when the test is complete, or when OperaIntervals.SELFTEST_TIMEOUT is reached.
